data.description: Welcome to Groves! This adorable 2 bed room, 2 bath , 2 car garage is the perfect starter house or home for those looking to downsize! The living room is open to the kitchen, providing ample space for everyone! The kitchen has granite counter tops, built in microwave, electric stove and oven, refrigerator, and a farmhouse sink. The bedrooms have carpet flooring and large closets. The 2 car garage is currently converted to a "man cave" but can be converted back to a regular garage. The large back yard host a 11x9.5 covered patio and a 12x20 shed with a wood privacy fence.
